 \begin{align} F_X(x)&=\int_0^xf(t)\ dt\\ \text{Pr}[X\le x]&=\int_0^x e^{-t}\ dt\\ &=-\left.e^{-t}\right|_{t=0}^x\\ &=1-e^{-x}. \end{align} 
